{"tid":2357403,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳菊：美麗島大審，我始終相信無罪。請國際的朋友，繼續撐香港。","createTime":"2021-01-07T11:44:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T12:13:46.000Z","uid":261647,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"0cd83c933cf4f98a9d509358fb44dab722229808","tid":2357403,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T11:44:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/kikuChen/posts/10158026785047405\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FkikuChen%2Fposts%2F10158026785047405&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6z4eonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=28935d74\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/kikuChen/posts/10158026785047405</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：陳菊(花媽)<br />\n<br />\n在黑暗中，我們堅持走向人權的光。<br />\n<br />\n當年美麗島大審中，我始終相信自己無罪，因為我們追求的人權信念，是跨越國界的普世價值，也獲得世界民主陣營的聲援。<br />\n<br />\n我要向香港的朋友們說，面對今日的大逮捕，請堅持追求人權的信念、相信自由的珍貴。<br />\n<br />\n請國際上所有關心人權的朋友，像當年支持台灣追求民主化，請繼續撐香港。"},{"pid":"c32cd104489fe4d6f589941b526757e8d8917d7e","tid":2357403,"uid":39710,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T11:44:58.000Z","msg":"花媽真係好堅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ac00e900035cac85b955228af14c5f1e82a5239","tid":2357403,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T11:46:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df8865ec684f7470605b7240e365b0e93f3a2ae4","tid":2357403,"uid":8014,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T11:46:38.000Z","msg":"1979年，陳菊在美麗島事件成為政治犯，當時曾一度被國民黨以「叛亂罪」起訴，該罪的唯一刑罰為死刑，因此曾寫下著名的「給台灣人民的遺書」。後在國際壓力下，當局改判有期徒刑，[7][8]陳菊在監獄服刑六年多後獲釋。"},{"pid":"b86ee0e22a4dd1055aaaadb2e492ee0ab788eeaa","tid":2357403,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T11:49:52.000Z","msg":"菊姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bc8fee4956d32a4e865767e461fa53bf5f0aaf2","tid":2357403,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T11:51:11.000Z","msg":"勁"},{"pid":"6b4078644867c933ca85795862ffd81cb94f891d","tid":2357403,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T11:52:29.000Z","msg":"佢篇遺書真係好癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"862c98d2b2663c14b9435f5b2f8691af0225d8ed","tid":2357403,"uid":228868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T11:53:13.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b41dd6f67867dfd3158dcff6e994cb3dc4743acb","tid":2357403,"uid":6435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T11:55:02.000Z","msg":"香港民族既分叉路"},{"pid":"0cb581105acf0e4e21f8e56e0a342d959dfdfa08","tid":2357403,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T11:57:17.000Z","msg":"當時敢反國民黨真係要好大勇氣,小小嘢都死刑"},{"pid":"accb43900d6095d39d90c3c078090f3d7f0d4808","tid":2357403,"uid":109713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T11:58:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ac73af482a978277c8316a0c6eea706c079a2d90","tid":2357403,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T12:02:23.000Z","msg":"「美麗島事件」本身, 就係台灣人的歷史試練<br />\n<br />\n香港只係遲咗40年"},{"pid":"5561e992ed0d145dd5e1202aa1311010be28f3ff","tid":2357403,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T12:04:59.000Z","msg":"同周庭一樣"},{"pid":"49100a8cbb7df761c90f0b0e28ef97227681c3c6","tid":2357403,"uid":91721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T12:13:46.000Z","msg":"花媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}